1. Imam *pedeset* novčića u džepu. (I have *fifty* coins in my pocket.)
2. Prošle nedelje sam pročitao *pedesetu* knjigu o istoriji Srbije. (Last week I read the *fiftieth* book about the history of Serbia.)
3. Moj deda je prošao *pedeset* kilometara peške da bi došao kući. (My grandfather walked *fifty* kilometers to get home.)
4. Ovaj grad je udaljen *pedeset* kilometara odavde. (This city is *fifty* kilometers away from here.)
5. *Pedeset* ljudi je bilo na koncertu sinoć. (There were *fifty* people at the concert last night.)
6. U kompletu ima *pedeset* olovaka različitih boja. (The set includes *fifty* pens of different colors.)
7. Da biste dobili popust, morate kupiti *pedeset* ili više proizvoda. (To get a discount, you have to buy *fifty* or more products.)
8. Većina zgrada u ovom kvartu je izgrađena pre *pedeset* godina. (Most of the buildings in this neighborhood were built *fifty* years ago.)
9. On je prodao svoj stari automobil za *pedeset* hiljada dinara. (He sold his old car for *fifty* thousand dinars.)
10. Svako jutro trčim *pedeset* krugova oko stadiona. (Every morning I run *fifty* laps around the stadium.)

(Note: The * symbol was used to highlight the word "pedeset" in each sentence.)